        "Id" : "forcedevent_co_HYR_219d_nationalAlliances_Marik",
        "Name" : "National Alliances",
        "Details" : "Darius rushes to the bridge from one of the hatches. \"Commander, tensions between [[TGT_MW,{TGT_MW.Callsign}]] and [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] appear to have turned for the worse! [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] can't be found anywhere on the DropShip and the logs report that one airlock was opened but it's impossible to know who was responsible.\"\r\n\r\nSumire intervenes. \"Both MechWarriors had a long standing known feud but it is also possible that this was just an accident. Not the first time a space rookie accidently jettisons {TGT_MW.Gender?Male:himself|Female:herself|NonBinary:theirselves} to space.\"\r\n\r\n\"{TGT_MW.Gender?Male:He|Female:She|NonBinary:They} {TGT_MW.Gender?Male:claims|Female:claims|NonBinary:claim} to have been with [[TRT_MW,{TRT_MW.Callsign}]] during the period just before [[TGT_MW,{TGT_MW.Callsign}]]\". Darius adds.\r\n\r\n\"Ah! Both of those MechWarriors seem to be spending a lot of time together nowadays. Does seem that someone might be replicating national rivalries onboard this company, since [[TGT_MW,{TGT_MW.Callsign}]] and [[TRT_MW,{TRT_MW.Callsign}]] are both from [[DM.Factions[faction_Marik],Free Worlds League]] and the [[DM.Factions[faction_Kurita],Draconis Combine]], while [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] comes from the [[DM.Factions[faction_Steiner],Lyran Commonwealth]] \". Yang's remark catches a few on the bridge off-guard.\r\n\r\n\"If we ignore this, we risk more of these 'incidents' taking place in the future. But taking a harsher position also has risks. How would you like to proceed Commander?",
        "Icon" : "uixTxrSpot_DailyBriefing.png"
    },
