                        "Id" : "outcome_1_1",
                        "Name" : "MW confesses",
                        "Details" : "You, Darius and Yang look at {TRT_MW.Callsign}, who is floating in zero-g gravity inside the airlock chamber where {SCN_MW.Callsign} reportedly disappeared. \r\n\r\n\"See, {TRT_MW.FirstName}, the problem with your story is that you and {TGT_MW.FirstName} both claim to have spent hours together, but there are several gaps missing.\" You pause to look at Yang, who nods towards you.\r\n\r\n\"There's something stinky in this DropShip, so unless your alibis start smelling better, we are going to start testing this airlock to make sure accidents don't happen again in the future.\" A small electronic display turns from green to red, as the air inside the chamber starts venting to space.\r\n\r\nTwo minutes later, {TRT_MW.Callsign} confesses over the intercom that {TGT_MW.Callsign} had asked {TGT_MW.Gender?Male:him|Female:her|NonBinary:their} to cover {TGT_MW.Gender?Male:his|Female:her|NonBinary:their} story but denies knowing  {TGT_MW.Gender?Male:him|Female:her|NonBinary:their} intentions towards {SCN_MW.Callsign}.\r\n\r\n\"{TGT_MW.FirstName} might have been a Kurita, but {TGT_MW.Gender?Male:he|Female:she|NonBinary:they} didn't deserve to die like this.\"",
