                        "Name" : "MW found",
                        "Details" : "\"I wasn't easy, but I realized that it would be possible to try to use the <i>Hysteria</i>'s sensors to locate {SCN_MW.Callsign} along our previous flight path, considering the position of the airlock in the DropShip.\" She punches a few keys on her electronic notepad.\r\n\r\n\"Luckly for {SCN_MW.Gender?Male:him|Female:her|NonBinary:their}, it appears that {SCN_MW.Gender?Male:he|Female:she|NonBinary:they} was wearing an EVA suit since we picked up the distress beacon. We can't reach her {SCN_MW.Gender?Male:his|Female:her|NonBinary:their} on radio, so we won't be sure of her status until we rescue her.\"\r\n\r\nSeveral hours later, {SCN_MW.Callsign} is at the MedBay recovering from dehydratation, laying on the bed while you and Darius stand on {SCN_MW.Gender?Male:his|Female:her|NonBinary:their} flanks.\r\n\r\n\"I'm sorry for all the mess I caused, Commander. I liked using that airlock for some quiet space walks since I knew the security system wasn't working, and sometimes others would join me.\"",
